title: Leonard Miller
text:
Was doubtful that my order would be fill without hassle but it was. A type o on my part was corrected with no problem at all. The courtesy that was exhibited was not surpassed by anyone. Thanks for your help and fast service. I will definitely recommend you all to everyone I know. Will order again in the future. Thanks a bunch.
Leonard Miller
